{
  "stem": "21349.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This man didn't know very much about bicycles, and didn't know very much about repair.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father taught him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And many people came to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But actually, he sent them over to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because he couldn't do the work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This went on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then they told this man, who was an member of the Nazi party, and those people who had an early number in the Nazi Party got priority.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He told the the man-- they told this man to build a wall next to our house so high that our window on the second floor was three quarters covered.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he took away all of our yard, which we had there and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They did this, so they showed it by doing all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- they sent people to our business buying things, and later on these things were stolen, which wasn't even true.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They tried to sell us stolen merchandise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We never bought that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean they did a lot of tricks and so forth, you see to get the Jews into prison.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I know one classmate of mine went to prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he was suspected of being a Communist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was in the oberrealschule till 1936.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At one time, in the beginning, the teachers came into the school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Germany there is a-- a custom, because German teachers are called officials.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how it is here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when the teacher comes in, everyone has to stand up and give a greeting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the teacher leaves, everyone stands up and give a greeting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have two kinds of greetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They have what they called a Hitler greeting and an German greeting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German greeting is like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Hitler greeting is like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
